        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This tower shield (Hardness 5, HP 20, BT 10) sports a bright red front with a gold inlay of an eagle. While it looks unassuming, this shield can protect not only yourself but also those behind you.",
